verbs.description: disbowel (third-person singular simple present disbowels, present participle disboweling or disbowelling, simple past and past participle disboweled or disbowelled)

examples: […]  a great Oke drie and dead, /  […]  / Whose foote in ground hath left but feeble holde; / But halfe disbowel'd lies aboue the ground,  […]
